{"TopicId":216107,"ForumId":131,"TopicTitle":"[Cancelled] Kerbal Space Program: Odyssey","CreatedByName":"Resonant","CreatedById":228347,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-31T20:06:22Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Resonant","CreatedById":228347,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-31T20:06:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\nPlease delete thread.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222024-07-25T05:33:23Z\u0022 title=\u002207/25/2024 05:33  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 dy\u0022\u003EThursday at 05:33 AM\u003C/time\u003E by Resonant\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EProject Cancelled\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"FL-T400","CreatedById":166421,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-31T21:46:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe general opinion of the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Realism Overhaul (mod)\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Realism Overhaul (mod)\u0022\u003ERO\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E team is that starting on something this big this early into KSP 2\u0027s development will likely be a fool\u0027s errand. Best of luck and I\u0027m certainly hoping you will be successful, but waiting for a stable modding API and starting with porting some of the more foundational mods like \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Module Manager (mod)\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Module Manager (mod)\u0022\u003EMM\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E, \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Ferram Aerospace Research (mod)\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Ferram Aerospace Research (mod)\u0022\u003EFAR\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E, or \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Real Solar System (mod)\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Real Solar System (mod)\u0022\u003ERSS\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E might give you a better chance of success. \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Realism Overhaul (mod)\u0022\u003ERO\u003C/abbr\u003E was created by a large team over 10 years, so make sure you aren\u0027t biting off more than you can chew.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-03-31T21:54:37Z\u0022 title=\u002203/31/2023 09:54  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 31, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by FL-T400\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EAdded another thing\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Resonant","CreatedById":228347,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-31T22:00:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224267802\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022216107\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221680299210\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022166421\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022FL-T400\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n15 minutes ago, FL-T400 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe general opinion of the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Realism Overhaul (mod)\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Realism Overhaul (mod)\u0022\u003ERO\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E team is that starting on something this big this early into KSP 2\u0027s development will likely be a fool\u0027s errand. Best of luck and I\u0027m certainly hoping you will be successful, but waiting for a stable modding API and starting with porting some of the more foundational mods like \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Module Manager (mod)\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Module Manager (mod)\u0022\u003EMM\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E, \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Ferram Aerospace Research (mod)\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Ferram Aerospace Research (mod)\u0022\u003EFAR\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E, or \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Real Solar System (mod)\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Real Solar System (mod)\u0022\u003ERSS\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E might give you a better chance of success.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMany thanks and best of luck to the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Realism Overhaul (mod)\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Realism Overhaul (mod)\u0022\u003ERO\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E-Team aswell, we largly agree that starting this early is risky and we will most likely face many many issues along the way, however for now we\u0027re really just trying to get a lay of the land so to speak and coming up with a solid plan for what we plan for this mod to be. We\u0027re more focused now on exploring the games code and seeing whats possible. Nothing is concrete currently and we know that a large majority of pretty much anything we build now will be useless, but we\u0027re learning and waiting to get our hands on the API, then hope to ramp up development far more than it is currently.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-03-31T22:03:28Z\u0022 title=\u002203/31/2023 10:03  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 31, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Resonant\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Egrammar\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pat20999","CreatedById":229082,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-05-21T08:15:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think that this mod my should wait till 2024.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KerbolExplorer","CreatedById":177191,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-07-07T21:53:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWith the current state of KSP2, I can only wish you the best of luck on this project.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"davidy12","CreatedById":143411,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-07-08T00:11:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003EYEAHHHHHH...\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou might wanna put this on hold for a\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003Ewhile\u003C/strong\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Makrom","CreatedById":216152,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-01-01T19:56:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGreat, I\u00B4m already waiting for this, best of luck and have a great year\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Snafu225","CreatedById":143694,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-01-09T18:54:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224285667\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022216107\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221684656935\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022229082\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Pat20999\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 5/21/2023 at 10:15 AM, Pat20999 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think that this mod my should wait till 2024.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLet\u0027s go! Sorry I had to..\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Little 908","CreatedById":228185,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-01-13T00:07:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAre any \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Realism Overhaul (mod)\u0022\u003ERO\u003C/abbr\u003E/\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Real Solar System (mod)\u0022\u003ERSS\u003C/abbr\u003E modders working on this mod? Or is it a completely different team?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Infinite Aerospace","CreatedById":230192,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-01-17T10:33:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-conten